      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising 2001 BMW M3 (E46), a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally calibrated for optimal cam phasing. This specimen features a reinforced rear subframe\u2014addressing the platform's primary structural vulnerability\u2014and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with precise synchronizer engagement. The chassis maintains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Finished in original Alpine White, the exterior is free of clear-coat failure or panel gaps, while the interior boasts pristine Nappa leather and a functioning pixel-perfect instrument cluster. Exhaustive service records confirm a rigorous maintenance schedule, ensuring this M3 remains in peak mechanical and aesthetic form.",
