      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures the paint remains flawless. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, bolsters are firm, and the original floor mats are spotless. Every electronic component, from the advanced infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It features a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified master technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any road debris or corrosion. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a documented folder of every service interval.",
